'''Hazem Mastouri''' ({{langx|ar|حازم المستوري}}; born 18 June 1997) is a Tunisian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Striker (association football)|striker]] for Russian club [[FC Dynamo Makhachkala|Dynamo Makhachkala]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].

==Club career==
Mastouri began playing football in the amateur [[Tunisian Ligue 3]] with [[Degache|AS Degache]] in 2016. In 2020, he had a short stint with [[Tozeur|LPS Tozeur]]. This led to a move to the [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] side [[ES Métlaoui]] in 2021 where he stayed 2 and a half season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://al-ain.com/article/tunisia-national-team-hazem-mastouri|title=مِن عالم الهواة إلى منتخب تونس.. مَن هو حازم مستوري؟|date=8 November 2024|website=العين الإخبارية}}</ref> On 26 September 2023, he moved to the [[Iraq Stars League]] team [[Al-Najaf FC]] where he scored 10 goals.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.babnet.net/cadredetail-273901.asp|title=نادي النجف العراقي يتعاقد مع اللاعب التونسي حازم المستوري|website=Babnet}}</ref> On 15 August 2024, he transferred to [[US Monastir (football)|US Monastir]] on a 2-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%81-%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%B9%D9%85-%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%88%D9%81%D9%87-%D8%A8%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%82%D8%A9-%D8%AA%D9%88%D9%86%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%A9/1272171|title=النجف يدعم صفوفه بصفقة تونسية &#124; كووورة|website=www.kooora.com}}</ref>

On 17 August 2025, Mastouri signed with [[Russian Premier League]] club [[FC Dynamo Makhachkala|Dynamo Makhachkala]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Dynamo Makhachkala|url=https://dinamo-mx.ru/blog/2025/08/17/napadayushhij-hazem-masturi-pereshel-v-dinamo/|title=Нападающий Хазем Мастури перешел в "Динамо"|date=17 August 2025|access-date=18 August 2025|language=ru}}</ref>

==International career==
He debuted with the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]] in a 3–2 [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]] win over [[Madagascar national football team|Madagascar]] on 14 November 2024, helping his team qualify for the final competition with the win.<ref name="p032">{{cite web | title=Tunisia qualify for the 2025 AFCON in dramatic fashion | website=SuperSport | date=2024-11-14 | url=https://supersport.com/football/africa-cup-qual/news/75be85b8-e8e5-4404-8def-c40943a87378/tunisia-qualify-for-the-2025-afcon-in-dramatic-fashion | access-date=2025-06-03}}</ref>

